---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms & Conditions | Complete Health Peptides"
  description="Our terms and conditions outline the rules, guidelines, and legal agreements between our company and individuals who use our products and services."
>
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-secondary-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl">Our terms of service and legal agreements for using our products and services.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="mb-8">Our full terms and conditions are available in our documentation center. Please click the button below to view the complete terms.</p>
        
        <div class="flex justify-center my-8">
          <a 
            href="https://docs.chpeptides.com/legal/terms-conditions.html" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer" 
            class="bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-medium text-lg transition inline-flex items-center"
          >
            View Full Terms & Conditions
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>These terms and conditions outline the rules and regulations for the use of Complete Health Peptides's Website and products. By accessing this website and/or purchasing our products, we assume you accept these terms and conditions.</p>
        
        <h2>Research Use Only</h2>
        <p>All products sold by Complete Health Peptides are intended for laboratory research purposes only. None of the products are intended for human consumption or therapeutic use. By purchasing our products, you agree that they will be used exclusively for research purposes.</p>
        
        <h2>Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
        <p>Unless otherwise stated, we or our licensors own the intellectual property rights for all material on our website. All intellectual property rights are reserved.</p>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg my-8">
          <p class="font-semibold">For the complete details of our terms and conditions, please refer to our documentation center by clicking the button above.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>